long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Jelly Forest is a whimsical puzzle adventure that takes you deep into a magical, candy-colored forest filled with jiggly, adorable creatures. As you explore this vibrant world, you'll solve puzzles by matching and combining jelly creatures to clear paths, unlock hidden areas, and overcome tricky obstacles. Each level introduces new challenges and delightful surprises, with beautiful visuals and soothing sounds that make the journey through Jelly Forest as relaxing as it is fun. Collect stars, discover special power-ups, and uncover the secrets of the enchanted forest. Dive into a world where everything is sweet and squishy!
